"Ask T about Phoenix" â†’ "Email Todd Chen re: Phoenix Migration Project"
"Check the RFP board" â†’ "Review Monday.com RFP Pipeline (shared view)"
"Nudge on the grant"  â†’ "Send reminder to Sarah re: NRLP Grant Submission"
```

