## ğŸš€ Getting the Most From The Butler

### Best Practices

âœ… **Daily Routine:** Run `/morning` every morning at the same time  
âœ… **Communication Samples:** Teach Butler multiple email types (10+ samples ideal)  
âœ… **VIP List:** Maintain updated VIP contacts with preferences  
âœ… **Weekly Sync:** Review `/delegations` every Friday  
âœ… **Monthly Learning:** Add new communication patterns monthly  
âœ… **Backup:** Run `/update` before critical events  

### Pro Tips

ğŸ’¡ **Shorthand Mastery:** The more you use shorthand, the better Butler learns  
ğŸ’¡ **Context Building:** Share background on complex projects in `/context`  
ğŸ’¡ **Tone Diversity:** Provide email samples in different styles  
ğŸ’¡ **Delegation Patterns:** Butler learns your delegation style over time  
ğŸ’¡ **Time Blocking:** Use `/execute` with time-bound tasks for better tracking  

